transcript:
Customer: Hello?
Executive: Hello?
Customer: Hello? Sir, good afternoon. I am Parth speaking from IndiaMART.
Customer: Please.
Executive: Sir, actually, you had consumed some leads, you had discussed, we had discussed that day.
Customer: I am a little busy in that, sir, I am a little, I have another work, I am busy.
Executive: Okay sir, I had created your catalog, sir, I just wanted to take feedback from you.
Customer: Okay sir, I will tell you. Is there any other concern, sir?
Executive: Okay.
Executive: Sir, I am sending you a feedback regarding our side, sir, please kindly... Feedback, leave it, sir, but now I am busy with another work, I will talk to you later.
Executive: So, I can close this concern, if there is no issue for you, sir? Because I have not been able to talk to you for a long time.
Customer: Okay sir.
Executive: A feedback will come on mail, sir, please kindly check it once.
